Title: The Seven Husbands of Evelyn Hugo
Author: Taylor Jenkins Reid
My Review: Incredible! I was hooked from the first page to the last. Hollywood glamour, secrets, and a heartbreaking love story. 5 stars, no notes.

Title: The Silent Patient
Author: Alex Michaelides
My Review: The twist was so obvious and completely nonsensical. The characters were flat and I found the entire plot unbelievable. Do not recommend.

Title: It Ends with Us (It Ends with Us, #1)
Author: Colleen Hoover

Title: Normal People
Author: Sally Rooney
My Review: This book completely wrecked me in the best way possible. The characters felt so real.

Title: The Song of Achilles
Author: Madeline Miller
My Review: One of the most beautiful books I've ever read.
